Class ViewElementDefinition

  • java.lang.Object

    GlobalViewElementDefinition

    public class ViewElementDefinition
extends Object
implements ElementDefinition
    A ViewElementDefinition is an ElementDefinition containing transient properties, an ElementTransformer and two ElementFilters.
